data.description:
EXQUISITE WATER-VIEW PENTHOUSE - A VISTA ABOVE THE REST! Revel in the breathtaking panorama from your lofty perch 16 floors high. Witness the world paint itself in stunning sunsets, each evening an invitation to indulge in the privilege of penthouse living.This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo seamlessly merges modernity and elegance. Granite counters and sleek stainless-steel appliances elevate your culinary experiences, transforming everyday moments into extraordinary memories. As a resident of The Edge, your realm extends beyond your penthouse walls. Immerse yourself in the allure of resort-style living, with a pool and clubhouse that redefine leisure. Discover a gym that embodies the epitome of cutting-edge wellness, and a business center that caters to both productivity and convenience.

Parking becomes a breeze with covered garage access that brings you seamlessly to your domain. Inside, a sense of spaciousness is elevated by high ceilings, while a walk-out balcony extends an open invitation to enjoy the world from new heights.

VIEWS become your constant companion - an ever-changing masterpiece that graces every corner of your residence. And within your unit, modern comforts abound: an HVAC system assures ideal climate control.

This isn't just a penthouse; it's a canvas for a life lived vividly. So come, seize the opportunity to reside among the clouds, where each day is an ode to the sublime. Your penthouse journey awaits - a realm of views, luxury, and unwavering refinement.

This great home is located just minutes from fine shopping, dining and much more!
